Enum ModelType

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<ModelType>
      org.opensourcedea.dea.ModelType
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ModelType>
public enum ModelType
extends java.lang.Enum<ModelType>

An enum of the possible Model Types (e.g. CCR, SBM...). If new models are added to the library, they will have to be listed in this enum.

The enum lists, for each model, the model characteristics. These are - amongst others:

  • ModelOrientation (e.g. input/output oriented),
  • Efficiency type (e.g. mix or technical),
  • Return To Scale (CONSTANT, VARIABLE).

Author:
Hubert Virtos
